snippet: The Buckeyes, the defending national champions, were followed by Texas Christian, Alabama, Baylor and Michigan State. The SEC led all conferences with eight teams in the top 25.
abstract: Ohio State becomes first unanimous No 1 selection in Associated Press preseason college football poll.
lead_paragraph: The Buckeyes, the defending national champions, were followed by Texas Christian, Alabama, Baylor and Michigan State. The SEC led all conferences with eight teams in the top 25.

headline.main: Ohio State Is First Unanimous No. 1 in Preseason A.P. Poll
headline.print_headline: A.P. Voters All Agree: Buckeyes are No. 1
